Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:25.72,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}全てを恋で染めたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:30.05,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どんなデキゴトも超えてゆける強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.58,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}キミがボクにくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.07,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「大人になったらね」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.51,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ちょっと油断してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.41,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}キミの横顔をね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.38,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}みているのよ  まだ今でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.53,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね  気付いたら？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.82,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}同じ  眼の高さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.65,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}いつの間にか少女じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.69,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}驚くでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:21.95,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}因為有你的餘溫  七彩鈕扣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:25.72,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一切都染上戀愛的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:30.05,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}克服一切困難那堅強的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.58,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}也是你給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.07,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「長大之後呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.51,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}有點大意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.41,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}現在也看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.38,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.53,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你看  發現了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.82,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}個子已經一樣高了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.65,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不知不覺間稚氣已經褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.69,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}嚇了一跳吧？
