Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.08,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}幼い頃の小さなページ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:03.98,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もが夢見てる今も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:07.16,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}大人になれず凍えた日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.47,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}幸せそうに眠ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.83,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}何も見当たらない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.98,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}白い息だけが眩しく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:25.49,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}風に吹かれた服を　そっと支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.51,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}When  I  look  into  your  heart
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:14:00.08,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}年幼時那小小的一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:03.98,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}不管誰都依然在夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:07.16,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}那稚氣未脫而冷冰冰的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.47,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}如此幸福地沉睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.83,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}看不到任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:17.98,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}白色的氣息如此耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:25.49,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}風輕輕地吹入這衣服
